ownedNfts.title: Fall 2022: META-511
ownedNfts.description:
This is your access token to META-511: NFTs and the Metaverse, a free MOOC by the University of Nicosia (UNIC) and the world's first university course delivered on-chain and in the metaverse.

With this token in your wallet, you can participate in the course in OM (6529's Open Metaverse), as well as join the course discussion in the UNIC Discord server.

Course Information: 
https://www.unic.ac.cy/openmetaverse/mooc-nfts-metaverse/

Original artwork by 6529er

Ethereum Name Service (ENS) domains are secure domain names for the decentralized world. ENS domains provide a way for users to map human readable names to blockchain and non-blockchain resources, like Ethereum addresses, IPFS hashes, or website URLs. ENS domains can be bought and sold on secondary markets.
